trans-unit.source: Provides a way to determine which target controls can be extended by a particular extender control in the toolbox.
trans-unit.target: 提供一個方式來判斷哪些目標控制項可以透過工具箱 中的特定擴充項控制項來擴充。

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ExtenderControlToolboxItem.GetTargetControlTypes%2A> method returns the collection of target types.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ExtenderControlToolboxItem.GetTargetControlTypes%2A>方法會傳回目標類型的集合。</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ExtenderControlToolboxItem.GetTargetControlTypes%2A>

trans-unit.source: The collection is cached for performance by using the <xref:System.Drawing.Design.ToolboxItem.Properties%2A> dictionary.

If you write an extender control that implements <xref:System.Web.UI.IExtenderControl>, but that does not derive from <xref:System.Web.UI.ExtenderControl>, specify this type in the <xref:System.ComponentModel.ToolboxItemAttribute> attribute of your control.
trans-unit.target: 如果您撰寫實作的擴充項控制項<xref:System.Web.UI.IExtenderControl>，但不是衍生自<xref:System.Web.UI.ExtenderControl>，指定此類型中的<xref:System.ComponentModel.ToolboxItemAttribute>控制項的屬性。</xref:System.ComponentModel.ToolboxItemAttribute> </xref:System.Web.UI.ExtenderControl> </xref:System.Web.UI.IExtenderControl>
